<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type'/>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Are you happy today?</h1>

    <p>
      Hello <%= @user.display_name %>!
    </p>

    <p>
      <b>Please tell me how do you feel today. Are you happy?</b><br/>
      <% Answer.result_dictionary.each_pair do |k, v| %>
          <%= link_to v, @answer.api_link(k) %><br/>
      <% end %>
    </p>

    <p>
      Remember that you can always change your daily vote after<br/>
      something awesome happens, and view your votes for the past 30 days.<br/>
      To do this please <%= link_to 'login', new_user_session_url %>
    </p>

    <p>
      This is automatically generated email. Please do not answer it.
    </p>
</body>
</html>
